The '''Ansel Adams Award for Conservation Photography''', named in honor of [[United States|American]] [[photographer]] [[Ansel Adams]], is a [[photography]] award administered by the [[Sierra Club]]. The award "honor[s] photographers who have used their talents in [[Conservation movement|conservation efforts]]."<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sierraclub.org/awards/downloads/Award_sr.pdf | title = Ansel Adams Award Winners | publisher = Sierra Club | accessdate = 2009-11-21 }}</ref>
